creator: ThirdPlay
descriptionHtml:
Compete in 3D summer games. Select your country, customize your player and jump in one of the 22 sport events. You can choose between speed races or long and high jump and many others. If you prefer water sports, you will have many options among free style, backstroke or butterfly swimming.

Test yourself by participating to the single event competition and, when you feel confident enough, take it to the next level and contend for the primacy in the Online games. You will compete with other players for the gold medal!

Be careful, to win medals you need to prove SPECIAL SKILLS: your performance for each of the 22 sports depends on a side game which will require you to be skillful in launching a ball at a proper distance, drive a disc to bounce a ball as many times as possible and others. This is not a game for everyone but only for the special skilled players. Are you one of them ?

Features:
22 sport events
3D graphics and animations.
Online games
Training session
7 levels

Compete in 3D summer games. Select your country, customize your player and jump in one of the 22 sport events. You can choose between speed races or long and high jump and many others. If you prefer water sports, you will have many options among free style, backstroke or butterfly swimming.

Test yourself by participating to the single event competition and, when you feel confident enough, take it to the next level and contend for the primacy in the Online games. You will compete with other players for the gold medal!

Be careful, to win medals you need to prove SPECIAL SKILLS: your performance for each of the 22 sports depends on a side game which will require you to be skillful in launching a ball at a proper distance, drive a disc to bounce a ball as many times as possible and others. This is not a game for everyone but only for the special skilled players. Are you one of them ?

Features:
22 sport events
3D graphics and animations.
Online games
Training session
7 levels

title: Athlete Skill Summer Games

creator: ThirdPlay
descriptionHtml:
Want to feel like a pro athlete? Now you can with Athlete Skill Summer Games! Enjoy a total of 22 fun competitive sports in 3D and reach the top of the leaderboard! If you want to compete in athletic sports like speed races, jumping events like the high jump, water sports, and more, this is the game for you. Turn into a runner, athletic jumper, swimmer, or any athlete of your choice.
Test your speed, endurance, and determination in the single-event competition. As you gain more experience and strength, compete for the gold medal with players from around the world!

FUN SUMMER ATHLETICS
Athlete Skill Summer Games include a variety of athletics. Games you can select from include track and field events, such as sprinting, or even water sports. Choose from different swimming strokes, such as freestyle, butterfly, or backstroke. To be successful and win, you must practice and master the featured side game. Will you be able to beat these competitive sports? Try and find out!

FOR ALL WILLING COMPETITORS
This game is meant for anyone who wants to compete and win! Whether you are a sports enthusiast, athlete, or simply a fan of summer sports games, these are the athletics to compete on! This app is a perfect summer game for kids, where they will enjoy single-player sports, gymnastics, throwing sports, and more!

EASY TO MASTER YOUR ATHLETIC PROWESS
People love championship games and climbing the ranks to hone their skills. This app is no ordinary fitness game that makes you feel like a basic summer runner. Athlete Skill Summer Games is a 3D competitive sports game to build your prowess and make you feel like one of the speed stars! Track and field games are fun to play, and you will enjoy developing your skills with the featured side game. Mastering this game takes some practice but is easy overall. You will feel like an athletic champion playing this game!

SUMMER GAMES- 3D GRAPHICS & ANIMATION
Enjoy top sports gameplay in 3D graphics & animation. Running track games and other athletic, physical games aren’t all made in basic 2D graphics anymore. Enjoy a cinematic view of the stadium at the beginning of the match. Then enjoy victory ceremonies and be proud of your win!
Not to mention, you can customize your 3D character to your liking, making your athletic experience more personable.

THE ATHLETIC GAMES FOR YOU
An entertaining yet easy-to-master game. Do all types of sports activities, jump, swim, run! Athletic events and other features are meant to be enjoyed in this app! Play the best sporting events conveniently on your mobile device.

FEATURES (use bullets)
● 22 Sports Events- Enjoy a multitude of sports.
● 3D Graphics- Enjoy 3D animation and graphics. Forget about 2D graphics in this game.
● Auto-Save Feature- Never lose your progress!
● Easy-to-Learn- Enjoyable yet easy to master.
● Customize Your Character- Edit your 3D athlete
● Play Online- Play with friends and with competitors from around the world.
● 7 Difficulty Levels- Each event has 7 levels of difficulty you can play through.
● Training Help- Get athlete training for several sports.
● Constantly Updating- Experience
